<mvc:View controllerName="gourmeo.resources.main.controllers.ItemManagement" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
    xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form"
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">

    <Page title="{i18n>itemMgmtPageTitle}" id="pageItemsMgmt" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress" noDataText="{i18n>tableItemsNoData}">
        <headerContent>
            <Button icon="sap-icon://add" press="onAddItemPress" />
            <Button icon="sap-icon://refresh" press="onRefreshItemsPress" />
        </headerContent>
        <content>
            <Table id="tblPartnerProducts"
                inset="false"
                items="{PartnerPrdCollection>/ProductCollection}" >
                <columns>
                    <Column>
                        <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnItem}" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column>
                        <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnDesc}" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column>
                        <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnResp}" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column>
                        <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnAux}" />
                    </Column>
                    <Column>
                        <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnCurReview}" />
                    </Column>
                </columns>
                <items>
                    <ColumnListItem>
                        <cells>
                            <Text text="{PartnerPrdCollection>id}" />
                            <Text text="{PartnerPrdCollection>description}" />
                            <Text text="" />
                            <Text text="" />
                            <Text text="" />
                        </cells>
                    </ColumnListItem>
                </items>
            </Table>
        </content>
    </Page>

</mvc:View>